videos.headline: Boyd breaks off 74-yard TD run
videos.description: Rakeem Boyd gets loose for a 74-yard touchdown run to give Arkansas an early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Boyd breaks off 74-yard TD run) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bowden fills in at QB for UK, leads Wildcats to victory
videos.description: Kentucky WR Lynn Bowden Jr. fills in at quarterback and gives the Wildcats the lead with a 24-yard touchdown run.
